Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs-3\pos(622.4,653)}Salamander
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死啦~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs-3\an8\shad0}（請稍候）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,變成大人真是太可悲了
